        p Italy has certainly won my heart, forever, irreversible. So much that everytime I think about going on holiday I always think about going back there. It has so much to offer. For example, after visiting Florence I could not imagine there will be something else that could mesmerize me as much. Siena proved me wrong. This small town it's so well preserved that it feels like stepping back a few centuries.

